{"type":"message","id":"04c32888","parentId":"136bed03","timestamp":"2026-07-05T19:23:35.605Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The boss is asking me to investigate two issues in the AstroHub project:\n\n1. Day/Night mode and IR filter - two 3-position toggle switches that don't work (nothing lights up, can't switch). Requirements: make them switchable and reflect the current device settings.\n\n2. Slow shutter setting - dropdown doesn't take effect, always stays at default *4 regardless of selection.\n\nI need to:\n1. Look at the console.html code for these switches\n2. Check the backend code (router.py, etc.) for the API endpoints\n3. Read the ISAPI development docs for correct API usage\n4. Provide a fix report\n\nLet me start by reading the relevant files.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_b9372acc1afc4e2abb3a9558","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"D:\\SDK\\HIK SDK\\ISAPI开发指南_球型网络摄像机_DF球机20261205051227\\ISAPI开发指南_球型网络摄像机_DF球机\" -Recurse | Select-Object FullName"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_979672f5dcb849c39480880f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"dayNight|irFilter|daynight|ir_filter|日夜|IR|slowShutter|慢快门|SlowShutter\" -Context 3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":319,"cacheRead":18884,"cacheWrite":6323,"totalTokens":25532,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783279408245,"responseId":"msg_f334362b-0872-4786-8261-abbf23a43da7"}}
