{"type":"message","id":"905c5c31","parentId":"caed0b48","timestamp":"2026-07-05T19:25:01.999Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to read the actual router.py code for the filter endpoints and the DSS endpoints to understand the exact implementation. Let me also read the ISAPI documentation to understand what the correct ISAPI endpoints should be.\n\nLet me now read:\n1. The full router.py filter endpoint code (around lines 3666-3764)\n2. The full router.py DSS endpoint code (around lines 3767-3832)\n3. The ISAPI docs\n\nLet me also check what `client.put(\"/Image/channels/1\", xml_str)` does for the filter - I need to understand the ISAPI filter endpoint.\n\nFrom the code I can already see:\n1. **Filter endpoint**: PUT to `/Image/channels/1` with XML containing `dayNightMode` and `irCutFilter`\n2. **DSS endpoint**: PUT to `/Image/channels/1/DSS` with XML containing `<DSS><enabled>...</enabled><DSSLevel>...</DSSLevel></DSS>`\n\nThe issues:\n1. **Day/Night and IR Cut**: Frontend calls `apiPost` (POST method) but the backend is registered as PUT (`@api_router.put`). Let me verify this.\n\nLooking at the frontend code:\n```javascript\nfunction setDayNightMode(mode) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/filter', { dayNightMode: mode })\n```\n\nIt's using `apiPost` (POST), but the backend has:\n```python\n@api_router.put(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/filter\", summary=\"设置滤镜和日夜模式\", tags=[\"Image\"])\nasync def set_filter_settings(device_id: str, body: dict) -> dict:\n```\n\n**This is the first bug!** Frontend sends POST, but backend expects PUT. The POST request would get a 405 Method Not Allowed, so the switch never updates.\n\nWait, but `loadFilterStatus` uses `apiGet` which should work for GET. Let me check the GET endpoint:\n```python\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/filter\", summary=\"获取滤镜和日夜模式\", tags=[\"Image\"])\nasync def get_filter_settings(device_id: str) -> dict:\n```\n\nSo the GET should work for loading the status. The issue with switches not lighting up might be because:\n- The GET returns `dayNightMode` and `irCutFilter` values\n- But the values returned from ISAPI might not match what the frontend expects\n\nFor example, the ISAPI might return \"daytime\" instead of \"day\", or \"night\" might be \"night\" vs something else. The `updateSwitchHighlight` function compares `btn.dataset.value === selectedValue`, and the buttons have values \"day\", \"night\", \"auto\" for dayNight and \"on\", \"off\", \"auto\" for IR cut.\n\nNow for the slow shutter issue:\nThe frontend `setSlowShutter` sends `{ dss_level: val }` via PUT. The backend processes it correctly. But wait - let me check if the frontend is actually calling the right thing.\n\n```javascript\nfunction setSlowShutter(val) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    apiPut('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/slow-shutter', { dss_level: val }).then(function(r) {\n```\n\nThis looks correct. The backend:\n```python\n@api_router.put(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter\", summary=\"设置慢快门\", tags=[\"Image\"])\nasync def set_slow_shutter(device_id: str, body: dict) -> dict:\n    ...\n    dss_level = body.get(\"dss_level\", \"\")\n    ...\n    xml_str = '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>' + chr(10) + '<DSS version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">' + chr(10) + '  <enabled>' + enabled + '</enabled>' + chr(10) + '  <DSSLevel>' + level_str + '</DSSLevel>' + chr(10) + '</DSS>'\n    put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/DSS\", xml_str)\n```\n\nLet me now check what ISAPI actually expects. Let me read the ISAPI documentation.\n\nActually, let me first check the actual ISAPI doc xlsx files. The filenames were garbled, let me try to read them.\n\nWait, xlsx files can't be read as text. Let me check if there are any HTML/XML/text format docs available. Or maybe I should look at the ISAPI docs for Image related endpoints.\n\nLet me check what files are in the SDK directory more carefully.\n\nActually, the main issue might be:\n1. **Day/Night & IR Cut**: Frontend uses `apiPost` (POST) but backend uses `@api_router.put` (PUT) → 405 error\n2. **Slow shutter**: Need to check if the DSS endpoint XML format is correct\n\nLet me read the full router.py filter endpoint code to verify.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me read the exact backend endpoints and check the ISAPI documentation.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4ce5a5a92f8b4b99b94dc358","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":170,"offset":3666,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_5916d7ee22ed4852a35e4777","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"D:\\SDK\" -Recurse -Include \"*.htm\",\"*.html\",\"*.xml\",\"*.txt\",\"*.md\",\"*.pdf\" -Depth 3 2>$null | Select-Object FullName"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":1324,"cacheRead":25207,"cacheWrite":16981,"totalTokens":43518,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783279474047,"responseId":"msg_a1381606-8063-44fa-b8bb-2c288fdbe2a2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c02bb2ac","parentId":"905c5c31","timestamp":"2026-07-05T19:25:02.466Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_4ce5a5a92f8b4b99b94dc358","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n# === 滤镜与日夜模式 (v8.43) ===\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/filter\", summary=\"获取滤镜与日夜模式\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_filter_settings(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取当前 dayNightMode 和 irCutFilter 设置。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取滤镜设置失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n        day_night = \"unknown\"\r\n        ir_cut = \"unknown\"\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag == \"dayNightMode\":\r\n                day_night = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\r\n            elif tag == \"irCutFilter\":\r\n                ir_cut = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\r\n\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": True,\r\n            \"data\": {\r\n                \"dayNightMode\": day_night,\r\n                \"irCutFilter\": ir_cut\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取滤镜设置异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.put(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/filter\", summary=\"设置滤镜与日夜模式\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_filter_settings(device_id: str, body: dict) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置 dayNightMode 和/或 irCutFilter。\r\n\r\n    请求体:\r\n        {\"dayNightMode\": \"day|night|auto\", \"irCutFilter\": \"on|off|auto\"}\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    day_night = body.get(\"dayNightMode\", \"\")\r\n    ir_cut = body.get(\"irCutFilter\", \"\")\r\n\r\n    # 先 GET 当前完整 XML，再修改对应字段后 PUT\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取当前设置失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        xml_str = resp.xml\r\n        import re\r\n\r\n        if day_night:\r\n            xml_str = re.sub(\r\n                r'(<dayNightMode>)[^<]*(</dayNightMode>)',\r\n                f'\\\\g<1>{day_night}\\\\g<2>',\r\n                xml_str\r\n            )\r\n        if ir_cut:\r\n            xml_str = re.sub(\r\n                r'(<irCutFilter>)[^<]*(</irCutFilter>)',\r\n                f'\\\\g<1>{ir_cut}\\\\g<2>',\r\n                xml_str\r\n            )\r\n\r\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1\", xml_str)\r\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            log_info(\"image\", \"filter\", {\"device\": device_id, \"dayNight\": day_night, \"irCut\": ir_cut})\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"滤镜设置成功\"}\r\n        else:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置失败: HTTP {put_resp.status_code}\"}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置滤镜异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n# === 慢快门 DSS (v8.45) ===\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter\", summary=\"获取慢快门设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_slow_shutter(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    mgr = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/DSS\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取DSS失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n        import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n        enabled = False\r\n        dss_level = \"\"\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag == \"enabled\":\r\n                enabled = (elem.text or \"\").strip().lower() == \"true\"\r\n            elif tag == \"DSSLevel\":\r\n                dss_level = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\r\n        return {\"success\": True, \"data\": {\"supported\": True, \"enabled\": enabled, \"dss_level\": dss_level}}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取DSS异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n@api_router.put(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter\", summary=\"设置慢快门\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_slow_shutter(device_id: str, body: dict) -> dict:\r\n    mgr = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    dss_level = body.get(\"dss_level\", \"\")\r\n    try:\r\n        if dss_level == \"off\":\r\n            enabled = \"false\"\r\n            level_str = \"*1\"\r\n        else:\r\n            enabled = \"true\"\r\n            level_str = dss_level\r\n        xml_str = '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>' + chr(10) + '<DSS version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">' + chr(10) + '  <enabled>' + enabled + '</enabled>' + chr(10) + '  <DSSLevel>' + level_str + '</DSSLevel>' + chr(10) + '</DSS>'\r\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/DSS\", xml_str)\r\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            log_info(\"image\", \"dss\", {\"device\": device_id, \"level\": dss_level})\r\n            try:\r\n                mac_clean = device_id.replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\r\n                if len(mac_clean) == 12:\r\n                    save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"slow_shutter\": {\"dss_level\": dss_level, \"enabled\": dss_level != \"off\"}})\r\n            except Exception:\r\n                pass\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"慢快门: \" + (\"关闭\" if dss_level == \"off\" else dss_level)}\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置失败: HTTP {put_resp.status_code}\"}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置DSS异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/settings-saved\", summary=\"获取设备保存的设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_saved_settings(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n\n[544 more lines in file. Use offset=3836 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783279502466}}
