{"type":"message","id":"1b12afd6","parentId":"5bd45ae7","timestamp":"2026-07-05T20:04:23.131Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user asked me to fix two issues in the astrohub console.html:\n1. Day/Night mode and IR filter switches not working - they need to be able to switch and show the current state\n2. Slow shutter settings not taking effect - always stuck at *4\n\nI've identified the root causes:\n1. Day/Night mode and IR filter: Frontend uses `apiPost` but backend expects `apiPut` (405 Method Not Allowed)\n2. Slow shutter: Frontend doesn't update the dropdown value after successful API call\n\nI've made the fixes:\n1. Changed `apiPost` to `apiPut` for both `setDayNightMode` and `setIRCutFilter`\n2. Added code to update the dropdown value after successful slow shutter setting\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Verify the changes were applied correctly\n2. Update the version number\n3. Test the changes\n4. Report to the user\n\nLet me continue with the fix process.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0dbc284d7d7b484583208e9a","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\main\\constants.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":111557,"output":260,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111817,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783281828849,"responseId":"chatcmpl-29955dec-08b4-9a0a-b637-361ca348e046"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5756f2d2","parentId":"1b12afd6","timestamp":"2026-07-05T20:04:23.137Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0dbc284d7d7b484583208e9a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\r\nM12 Unified Integration v1.0 - 全局常量定义\r\n\r\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nfrom __future__ import annotations\r\n\r\nfrom enum import Enum\r\nfrom pathlib import Path\r\n\r\n# === 版本与作者 ===\r\nVERSION = \"v8.48\"\r\nVERSION_NUM = \"8.15\"\r\nAUTHOR = \"雅痞张@南方天文\"\r\nPROJECT_NAME = \"MAIN\"\r\n\r\n# === 路径 ===\r\nBASE_DIR = Path(__file__).resolve().parent\r\n\r\n# === M1-M11 模块初始化顺序 ===\r\n# v7.12: 精简后保留的模块\r\n# 注意: device 模块已整合到 src/core/device_manager.py\r\nMODULE_ORDER = [\r\n    \"ptz\",\r\n    \"stream\",\r\n    \"calibration\",\r\n    \"database\",\r\n    \"websocket\",\r\n    \"ascom\",\r\n]\r\n\r\n\r\n# === 健康状态枚举 ===\r\nclass HealthStatus(Enum):\r\n    \"\"\"模块健康状态。\"\"\"\r\n    HEALTHY = \"healthy\"\r\n    DEGRADED = \"degraded\"\r\n    UNHEALTHY = \"unhealthy\"\r\n    UNKNOWN = \"unknown\"\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783281863137}}
