{"type":"message","id":"6d44c5b2","parentId":"02684deb","timestamp":"2026-07-05T20:15:09.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is reporting that:\n1. The day/night mode and IR filter switches still don't work - they want the triple-switch (三段式开关) to be properly highlighted, not meaningless buttons\n2. The slow shutter setting still doesn't take effect - clicking has no effect\n\nThey also mention \"按下还直接卡死\" (pressing it causes a freeze) which suggests a UI/JS error.\n\nLet me think about this more carefully. I changed `apiPost` to `apiPut`, but maybe the problem is:\n1. The `updateSwitchHighlight` function is not working properly\n2. Or the `loadFilterStatus` is not being called on page load\n3. Or the CSS for `.ts-btn.active` is missing\n\nLet me also reconsider the slow shutter issue. I added code to update the dropdown after setting, but the user says \"点了和没点没有任何区别\" which means clicking does nothing at all - not even an API call.\n\nWait, let me re-read the user's complaint more carefully:\n1. \"日夜转换，开关依然是没有亮起任何一个\" - Day/night and IR filter switches don't light up\n2. \"我要的是三段式开关，不是一堆无意义的按钮\" - They want the triple-switch to be visually marked, not just buttons\n3. \"按下还直接卡死\" - Pressing causes a freeze\n\nFor the freeze, I suspect the issue is that when the button is clicked, it calls `setDayNightMode(mode)` which now uses `apiPut` (correct), but the backend returns a 405 error because... wait, the backend is `@api_router.put`, so `apiPut` should work now.\n\nUnless... the freeze is caused by something else. Let me check if there are any JS errors.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The user is asking me to do a comprehensive investigation. Let me:\n\n1. Check the current state of console.html after my edits\n2. Verify the edit was applied correctly\n3. Check if there are JS errors (maybe the `apiPut` call is failing and causing a freeze)\n4. Check the CSS for `.ts-btn.active`\n5. Verify the slow shutter issue\n\nLet me read the current console.html to verify my edits were applied correctly, and then do a thorough analysis.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"明白，老板。立即全面排查。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:54","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"setDayNightMode|setIRCutFilter|setSlowShutter|apiPut|apiPost\" -Context 1,2 | Select-String \"function setDayNight|function setIRCut|function setSlowShutter|apiPut|apiPost\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":113272,"output":592,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113864,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783282485402,"responseId":"cht000d9f18@dx19f33eb6ab829c2503"}}
