{"type":"message","id":"9ddd51e2","parentId":"508f2002","timestamp":"2026-07-05T20:29:59.587Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:72","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<style>\r\n/* v7.30: 模块禁用样式 - 保留折叠展开功能 */\r\n.section-disabled .collapsible-content {\r\n    opacity: 0.4;\r\n    pointer-events: none;\r\n}\r\n.section-disabled .collapsible-header {\r\n    opacity: 0.6;\r\n}\r\n.section-disabled .collapsible-header:hover {\r\n    cursor: pointer;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* v6.02: 拨杆开关样式 */\r\n.toggle-switch {\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    display: inline-block;\r\n    width: 40px;\r\n    height: 22px;\r\n}\r\n.toggle-switch input {\r\n    opacity: 0;\r\n    width: 0;\r\n    height: 0;\r\n}\r\n.toggle-slider {\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    cursor: pointer;\r\n    top: 0;\r\n    left: 0;\r\n    right: 0;\r\n    bottom: 0;\r\n    background-color: #30363d;\r\n    transition: 0.3s;\r\n    border-radius: 22px;\r\n}\r\n.toggle-slider:before {\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    content: \"\";\r\n    height: 16px;\r\n    width: 16px;\r\n    left: 3px;\r\n    bottom: 3px;\r\n    background-color: #e0e6f0;\r\n    transition: 0.3s;\r\n    border-radius: 50%;\r\n}\r\ninput:checked + .toggle-slider {\r\n    background-color: #238636;\r\n}\r\n\n[1671 more lines in file. Use offset=416 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783283399587}}
