{"type":"message","id":"1b8c1d71","parentId":"6c4d0e3c","timestamp":"2026-07-05T20:33:36.742Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user hasn't said anything new. I completed the fixes and verified the syntax. Let me now provide a summary of what was fixed and ask the user to restart the service to test.\n\nAll fixes are complete:\n1. console.html: Added CSS for triple-switch, added .catch() error handling\n2. router.py: Wrapped sync ISAPI calls with asyncio.to_thread\n3. constants.py: Updated version to v8.50\n\nThe user said \"修复！精准修复！禁止绕弯路，禁止开发额外依赖脚本！备份后迭代版本！禁止过度开发\"\n\nI have:\n- Fixed the issues with minimal changes\n- Created backups\n- Updated version number\n- Verified syntax\n\nNow I should tell the user to restart the service and test.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**修复完成，版本 v8.50**\n\n### 修改内容\n\n**1. console.html（前端）**\n- ✅ 添加三段式开关 CSS（`.ts-btn`, `.ts-btn.active`）\n- ✅ `setDayNightMode` / `setIRCutFilter` / `setSlowShutter` 添加 `.catch()` 错误处理\n\n**2. router.py（后端）**\n- ✅ `get_filter_settings` / `set_filter_settings` / `get_slow_shutter` / `set_slow_shutter` — 同步 `client.get()` / `client.put()` 改为 `await asyncio.to_thread(...)`\n\n**3. constants.py**\n- ✅ VERSION v8.48 → v8.50\n\n### 重启测试\n\n请重启 Astrohub 服务后测试：\n1. 三段式开关 — 点击应高亮，不再卡死\n2. 慢快门 — 选择后 toast 提示成功，下拉菜单保持选中值"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":134251,"output":354,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134605,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783283593046,"responseId":"cht000d72f1@dx19f33fc34f029bb503"}}
