{"type":"message","id":"4f772560","parentId":"d21aec33","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:04:47.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板指出了一个问题：如果设备没有连接，为什么 Playwright 测试中能看到运动控制的设备信息？为什么 WASM 框体有设备的画面？\n\n让我回顾 Playwright 测试的结果：\n- screenshot_02_console.png 是 392KB，说明有完整的内容\n- 运动控制区域有 Pan/Tilt/Zoom 信息\n- WASM 播放器区域有画面\n\n这说明设备是连接的！让我重新检查 Playwright 测试的代码。\n\n回顾 verify_v850.py：\n```python\n# 导航到主控台\nawait page.goto(\"http://127.0.0.1:10280\", wait_until=\"networkidle\", timeout=15000)\nawait page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n```\n\n它直接导航到了主控台页面，然后等待。如果 AstroHub 已经连接了设备（之前的会话），那么 `window.connectedDevice` 应该是有值的。\n\n让我检查 Playwright 测试中是否有检查 `window.connectedDevice`：\n\n```python\n# 检查三段式开关是否存在\nday_night_switch = page.locator(\"#dayNightSwitch\")\nir_cut_switch = page.locator(\"#irCutSwitch\")\nslow_shutter = page.locator(\"#slowShutterSelect\")\n```\n\n但没有检查 `window.connectedDevice`。\n\n让我检查 `loadFilterStatus` 是否被调用了：\n\n从 console.html 的 HTML 结构来看，三段式开关在 HTML 中存在，但 `loadFilterStatus` 只在页面加载时调用一次（在 `loadAllImageParams` 中）。\n\n问题可能是：\n1. Playwright 导航到主控台页面时，`loadAllImageParams` 没有被调用（因为设备已经在之前的会话中连接了）\n2. 或者 `loadFilterStatus` 被调用了，但返回的数据没有正确更新按钮状态\n\n让我用 Playwright 检查：\n1. `window.connectedDevice` 是否有值\n2. `loadFilterStatus` 是否被调用\n3. 按钮的 class 是什么\n\n实际上，我应该直接问老板：设备是否连接了？如果连接了，那 Playwright 测试应该能验证按钮是否高亮。\n\n但是老板说\"如果没有连接设备，为什么运动控制可以读取到设备的信息？为什么WASM框体有设备的画面？\"\n\n这说明老板认为设备是连接的！\n\n让我用 Playwright 检查 `window.connectedDevice` 和按钮状态。\n明白了，老板。设备是连接的。让我用 Playwright 检查 `window.connectedDevice` 和按钮的实际状态。\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_195a3aa720c54c43bb939883","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"检查已连接设备状态\"\"\"\nimport asyncio\nfrom playwright.async_api import async_playwright\n\nasync def main():\n    async with async_playwright() as p:\n        browser = await p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n        page = await browser.new_page(viewport={\"width\": 1400, \"height\": 900})\n        \n        # 导航到主控台\n        await page.goto(\"http://127.0.0.1:10280\", wait_until=\"networkidle\", timeout=15000)\n        await page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n        \n        # 检查 window.connectedDevice\n        connected_device = await page.evaluate(\"window.connectedDevice\")\n        print(f\"window.connectedDevice: {connected_device}\")\n        \n        # 检查按钮状态\n        for switch_id in ['dayNightSwitch', 'irCutSwitch']:\n            switch = await page.query_selector(f'#{switch_id}')\n            if switch:\n                buttons = await switch.query_selector_all('.ts-btn')\n                print(f\"\\n{switch_id}:\")\n                for i, btn in enumerate(buttons):\n                    class_name = await btn.get_attribute('class')\n                    data_value = await btn.get_attribute('data-value')\n                    print(f\"  Button {i}: class='{class_name}', data-value='{data_value}'\")\n        \n        # 检查慢快门\n        slow_shutter = await page.query_selector('#slowShutterSelect')\n        if slow_shutter:\n            current_value = await slow_shutter.get_attribute('value')\n            print(f\"\\nslowShutterSelect value: {current_value}\")\n        \n        # 截图\n        await page.screenshot(path=\"check_device_status.png\", full_page=False)\n        print(\"\\nScreenshot saved: check_device_status.png\")\n        \n        await browser.close()\n\nasyncio.run(main())\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\check_device_status.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":1011,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":250196,"totalTokens":251213,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783285443266,"responseId":"msg_17348936-f10b-4e07-b636-16adf6fee118"}}
