{"type":"message","id":"49c89221","parentId":"96509938","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:08:18.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to check the code and find mismatches. Let me analyze what I found:\n\n1. **ISAPI field names** (from xlsx): `dayNightMode` and `ircutFilter`\n2. **Backend code** (router.py): uses `dayNightMode` and `irCutFilter` (capital C in irCutFilter)\n3. **HTML data-values**: `day/night/auto` and `on/off/auto`\n\nThe backend returns `\"dayNightMode\": \"unknown\"` and `\"irCutFilter\": \"unknown\"` - this means the XML parsing is not finding the elements!\n\nThe issue is:\n- ISAPI uses `ircutFilter` (lowercase)\n- Backend looks for `irCutFilter` (camelCase)\n\nSo the backend is looking for the wrong element name!\n\nI need to fix:\n1. Backend GET: Change `tag == \"irCutFilter\"` to `tag == \"ircutFilter\"`\n2. Backend PUT: Change the XML element name in the regex\n\nLet me check the exact code and fix it.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！后端返回 `\"dayNightMode\": \"unknown\"` 和 `\"irCutFilter\": \"unknown\"` — **解析完全失败了**！\n\nISAPI xlsx 里的字段名是 `ircutFilter`（小写 ircut），但后端代码用的是 `irCutFilter`（驼峰）。XML 元素名不匹配，所以解析出来全是 unknown。\n\n让我看后端代码并精准修复：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_68142cf0dd9d40e0b358a341","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":3666,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":395,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":158669,"totalTokens":159070,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783285685904,"responseId":"msg_fa3a0e99-2b52-4709-b664-92ea4946124c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"301b43fa","parentId":"49c89221","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:08:18.571Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_68142cf0dd9d40e0b358a341","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n# === 滤镜与日夜模式 (v8.43) ===\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/filter\", summary=\"获取滤镜与日夜模式\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_filter_settings(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取当前 dayNightMode 和 irCutFilter 设置。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = await asyncio.to_thread(client.get, \"/Image/channels/1\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取滤镜设置失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n        day_night = \"unknown\"\r\n        ir_cut = \"unknown\"\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n\n[684 more lines in file. Use offset=3696 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783285698571}}
