`IrcutFilterType`（值映射：auto/on/off）\n\n但老板说\"禁止过度开发\"，我应该：\n1. 只修改字段名不匹配的部分\n2. 不要重新设计逻辑\n3. 如果有字段不存在，就让它返回 unknown，但保证现有功能正确\n\n最精确的修复：\n1. 将后端 `tag == \"irCutFilter\"` 改为 `tag == \"IrcutFilterType\"`（或其他正确的字段名）\n2. 删除 `dayNightMode` 的查找（如果该字段不存在）\n3. 或者保留 `dayNightMode` 但让它继续返回 unknown（不影响现有功能）\n\n但是，前端有两个开关，后端需要返回两个值。如果只修改一个字段，另一个开关就无法工作。\n\n让我再看看 ISAPI 文档，看看是否有 `dayNightMode` 字段。\n\n实际上，我应该先告诉用户我发现了什么，然后问用户的意见。\n\n不，老板说\"禁止绕弯路\"。让我直接修复。\n\n最精确的修复：\n1. 修改后端，从 `<IrcutFilter>` 块中读取 `IrcutFilterType` 作为 `irCutFilter`\n2. 对于 `dayNightMode`，可能不存在对应的字段，需要单独处理\n\n让我先修复 `irCutFilter` 字段名的问题。\n\n等等，我需要在 `/Image/channels/1` 的 XML 中找到 `<IrcutFilter>` 块。从之前的搜索来看，它确实在 XML 中。\n\n但后端代码只做了简单的 `root.iter()` 遍历，没有处理嵌套结构。\n\n当前的解析代码：\n```python\nfor elem in root.iter():\n    tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\n    if tag == \"dayNightMode\":\n        day_night = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n    elif tag == \"irCutFilter\":\n        ir_cut = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n```\n\n这会在整个 XML 树中查找 `dayNightMode` 和 `irCutFilter`，但由于这些标签不存在，所以返回 unknown。\n\n实际的标签是：\n- `<IrcutFilterType>auto</IrcutFilterType>` - 这是 IR 滤镜类型\n- `<IrcutFilterAction>day</IrcutFilterAction>` - 这是当前 IR 滤镜动作\n\n所以，我应该将 `irCutFilter` 改为 `IrcutFilterType`，但值映射也需要调整：\n- 前端值：on, off, auto\n- ISAPI 值：auto, on, off（应该匹配）\n\n对于 `dayNightMode`，可能不存在对应的字段。我需要告诉用户这个字段可能不存在，或者询问用户如何处理。\n\n但老板说\"禁止绕弯路\"。让我直接修复我能确认的问题。\n\n最精确的修复：\n1. 将 `irCutFilter` 改为 `IrcutFilterType`（值映射相同）\n2. 对于 `dayNightMode`，暂时保持原样（返回 unknown），因为该字段不存在于 `/Image/channels/1` 端点\n\n但这会影响\"日夜模式\"开关的功能。如果该字段不存在，这个开关就无法工作。\n\n让我再仔细看看 XML，是否有其他类似的字段。\n\n从搜索结果：\n- `nightToDayFilterLevel` - 夜到日滤镜级别\n- `IrcutFilterType` - IR 滤镜类型（auto/on/off）\n- `IrcutFilterAction` - IR 滤镜动作（day/night）\n\n没有 `dayNightMode`。\n\n所以结论：\n1. `dayNightMode` 字段不存在于 `/Image/channels/1` 端点\n2. `irCutFilter` 字段也不存在，实际字段是 `IrcutFilterType`\n\n修复方案：\n1. 修改后端代码，将 `irCutFilter` 改为 `IrcutFilterType`\n2. 对于 `dayNightMode`，让它继续返回 unknown，或者删除这个字段的查找\n\n但这样会只修复一个开关。对于\"日夜模式\"开关，如果没有对应的字段，需要：\n- 从 `IrcutFilterAction` 获取（但值是 \"day\"/\"night\"，不是 \"day\"/\"night\"/\"auto\"）\n- 或者从其他端点获取\n\n这涉及到重新设计，老板说\"禁止过度开发\"。\n\n让我想想最简单的修复方案：\n1. 只修复 `irCutFilter` → `IrcutFilterType` 的字段名不匹配\n2. 对于 `dayNightMode`，可能需要用 `IrcutFilterAction` 作为替代\n\n但 `IrcutFilterAction` 的值是 \"day\"/\"night\"，而前端按钮的值是 \"day\"/\"night\"/\"auto\"。值映射不一致。\n\n最简单的做法是：\n1. 将 `irCutFilter` 改为 `IrcutFilterType`（值都是 auto/on/off，映射相同）\n2. 对于 `dayNightMode`，可能不存在对应字段，让它继续返回 unknown\n\n这样：\n- IR 滤镜开关可以工作（通过 `IrcutFilterType`）\n- 日夜模式开关无法工作（因为字段不存在）\n\n但用户可能会问为什么日夜模式开关不工作。我需要说明原因。\n\n或者，我可以：\n1. 将 `dayNightMode` 也映射到 `IrcutFilterType`（但这会导致两个开关控制同一个值，不合理）\n\n我认为最正确的做法是：\n1. 修复 `irCutFilter` 字段名\n2. 说明 `dayNightMode` 字段不存在于当前端点\n3. 如果需要，可以单独调用 `/IrcutFilter` 端点获取\n\n但是，后端代码中，`set_filter_settings` 也是修改 `/Image/channels/1`，而不是单独的端点。\n\n让我重新看看 `set_filter_settings` 的逻辑：\n```python\nresp = await asyncio.to_thread(client.get, \"/Image/channels/1\")\nxml_str = resp.xml\n# 修改字段\nif day_night:\n    xml_str = re.sub(...)\nif ir_cut:\n    xml_str = re.sub(...)\nput_resp = await asyncio.to_thread(client.put, \"/Image/channels/1\", xml_str)\n```\n\n它 GET `/Image/channels/1` 获取完整 XML，修改后再 PUT 回去。\n\n但 `/Image/channels/1` 中不包含 `dayNightMode` 和 `irCutFilter` 字段，所以修改无效。\n\n正确的做法是：\n- 如果 `dayNightMode` 和 `irCutFilter` 不在 `/Image/channels/1` 中，需要单独调用其他端点\n- 或者，修改 `/IrcutFilter` 端点\n\n但我不确定 ISAPI 的正确做法是什么。\n\n根据 ISAPI 文档，`/Image/channels/1` 应该包含这些字段。但设备实际返回的 XML 中不包含。\n\n可能的原因：\n1. 设备固件版本不同，字段名不同\n2. 这些字段在 `/Image/channels/1` 中不存在，需要通过其他端点获取\n3. 这些字段被嵌套在其他结构中\n\n从 XML 来看，`<IrcutFilter>` 是一个独立的块，可能是一个独立的端点。\n\n实际上，Hikvision ISAPI 中，`/Image/channels/1/IrcutFilter` 是一个独立的端点，用于配置 IR 滤镜。\n\n所以，后端可能需要：\n1. GET `/Image/channels/1` 获取基本图像配置\n2. GET `/Image/channels/1/IrcutFilter` 获取 IR 滤镜配置\n3. PUT `/Image/channels/1/IrcutFilter` 设置 IR 滤镜配置\n\n但这涉及到重新设计后端逻辑，老板说\"禁止过度开发\"。\n\n最精确的修复方案：\n1. 修改后端 `get_filter_settings`，将 `irCutFilter` 改为 `IrcutFilterType`\n2. 修改后端 `set_filter_settings`，将 `irCutFilter` 改为 `IrcutFilterType`\n3. 对于 `dayNightMode`，让它继续返回 unknown（因为该字段不存在）\n\n但这会导致\"日夜模式\"开关不工作。用户可能需要重新考虑这个开关的实现。\n\n或者，我可以：\n1. 将 `dayNightMode` 映射到 `IrcutFilterAction`（但值不完全匹配）\n2. 将 `irCutFilter` 映射到 `IrcutFilterType`\n\n但 `IrcutFilterAction` 的值是 \"day\"/\"night\"，`IrcutFilterType` 的值是 \"auto\"/\"on\"/\"off\"。\n\n两个开关控制的是同一个 IR 滤镜的不同方面。\n\n我觉得最好的做法是：\n1. 修复 `irCutFilter` 字段名不匹配\n2. 告诉用户 `dayNightMode` 字段不存在，需要进一步确认\n\n但用户说\"禁止绕弯路\"。让我直接修复。\n\n最精确的修复：\n1. 修改 `get_filter_settings`：\n   - `tag == \"dayNightMode\"` → 删除（字段不存在）\n   - `tag == \"irCutFilter\"` → `tag == \"IrcutFilterType\"`\n2. 修改 `set_filter_settings`：\n   - `r'(<irCutFilter>)'` → `r'(<IrcutFilterType>)'`\n\n这样：\n- IR 滤镜开关可以工作（通过 `IrcutFilterType`）\n- 日夜模式开关返回 unknown（因为字段不存在）\n\n但这不完全解决用户的问题。\n\n等等，我注意到 `IrcutFilterAction` 的值是 \"day\"，而前端日夜模式按钮的值是 \"day\"/\"night\"/\"auto\"。\n\n也许 `dayNightMode` 应该映射到 `IrcutFilterAction`？但 `IrcutFilterAction` 的取值是 \"day\"/\"night\"（没有 \"auto\"）。\n\n如果用户选择 \"auto\"，`IrcutFilterAction` 应该是什么？\n\n这很复杂。让我重新思考。\n\n也许最正确的做法是：\n1. 对于\"日夜模式\"开关（day/night/auto）：\n   - 如果选\"day\"，设置 `IrcutFilterType` = \"on\"（IR滤镜开启？）\n   - 如果选\"night\"，设置 `IrcutFilterType` = \"off\"（IR滤镜关闭？）\n   - 如果选\"auto\"，设置 `IrcutFilterType` = \"auto\"\n\n但这不符合直觉。\n\n或者，\"日夜模式\"控制的是 `IrcutFilterAction`：\n- 选\"day\" → `IrcutFilterAction` = \"day\"\n- 选\"night\" → `IrcutFilterAction` = \"night\"\n- 选\"auto\" → 删除 `IrcutFilterAction` 或设置为其他值？\n\n但 `IrcutFilterAction` 是只读的（表示当前状态），不能设置。\n\n所以\"日夜模式\"开关应该控制的是 `IrcutFilterType`：\n- 选\"day\" → `IrcutFilterType` = \"on\"（强制开启 IR 滤镜，即夜视模式？不，应该是白天模式...）\n\n等等，我需要重新理解 Hikvision ISAPI 中 IR 滤镜的逻辑。\n\n在 Hikvision 相机中：\n- IR Cut Filter 在白天是关闭的（允许可见光进入）\n- IR Cut Filter 在夜间是开启的（阻挡可见光，允许红外光进入）\n\n所以：\n- `IrcutFilterType` = \"auto\" → 自动切换（根据光线条件）\n- `IrcutFilterType` = \"on\" → 强制开启（夜视模式）\n- `IrcutFilterType` = \"off\" → 强制关闭（白天模式）\n\n而 `IrcutFilterAction` = \"day\" → 当前是白天模式（IR滤镜关闭）\n`IrcutFilterAction` = \"night\" → 当前是夜间模式（IR滤镜开启）\n\n所以，\"日夜模式\"开关（day/night/auto）应该对应 `IrcutFilterType`：\n- \"day\" → `IrcutFilterType` = \"off\"\n- \"night\" → `IrcutFilterType` = \"on\"\n- \"auto\" → `IrcutFilterType` = \"auto\"\n\n而\"IR 滤镜\"开关（on/off/auto）也应该对应 `IrcutFilterType`：\n- \"on\" → `IrcutFilterType` = \"on\"\n- \"off\" → `IrcutFilterType` = \"off\"\n- \"auto\" → `IrcutFilterType` = \"auto\"\n\n两个开关控制的是同一个字段！这是不合理的。\n\n除非，\"日夜模式\"和\"IR 滤镜\"是两个不同的功能：\n- \"日夜模式\"控制相机的日夜模式（可能影响其他参数）\n- \"IR 滤镜\"控制 IR Cut Filter 的开关\n\n但在 ISAPI 中，这两个功能可能都是通过 `IrcutFilterType` 控制的。\n\n或者，\"日夜模式\"是通过 `IrcutFilter` 端点控制的，而\"IR 滤镜\"是通过其他端点控制的。\n\n我觉得我需要更多的信息来确定正确的做法。但老板说\"禁止绕弯路\"，我应该直接修复。\n\n最可能的解释是：\n- 后端代码期望的 `dayNightMode` 和 `irCutFilter` 字段不存在于 `/Image/channels/1` 端点\n- 实际字段是 `IrcutFilterType`（在 `<IrcutFilter>` 块中）\n- 后端需要修改来正确解析这些字段\n\n但两个开关控制同一个字段的问题无法通过简单修复解决。\n\n我认为最合理的做法是：\n1. 将 `irCutFilter` 改为 `IrcutFilterType`（用于 IR 滤镜开关）\n2. 将 `dayNightMode` 也映射到 `IrcutFilterType`（用于日夜模式开关）\n3. 但这样两个开关控制同一个值，不合理\n\n或者，也许 `dayNightMode` 应该映射到 `IrcutFilterAction`（只读状态）？\n\n我觉得最好的做法是：\n1. 修复 `irCutFilter` 字段名（改为 `IrcutFilterType`）\n2. 对于 `dayNightMode`，暂时让它继续返回 unknown\n3. 询问用户\"日夜模式\"开关应该对应哪个 ISAPI 字段\n\n但老板说禁止绕弯路。让我直接修复。\n\n最精确的修复（只改字段名，不改逻辑）：\n\n```python\n# get_filter_settings\nfor elem in root.iter():\n    tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\n    if tag == \"dayNightMode\":\n        day_night = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n    elif tag == \"IrcutFilterType\":\n        ir_cut = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n```\n\n但 `dayNightMode` 字段不存在，所以 `day_night` 永远是 \"unknown\"。\n\n```python\n# set_filter_settings\nif ir_cut:\n    xml_str = re.sub(\n        r'(<IrcutFilterType>)[^<]*(</IrcutFilterType>)',\n        f'\\\\g<1>{ir_cut}\\\\g<2>',\n        xml_str\n    )\n```\n\n这样 IR 滤镜开关应该可以工作，但日夜模式开关不行。\n\n这是我能做的最精确的修复，不涉及重新设计逻辑。\n\n但是，我还需要处理 `IrcutFilter` 块的嵌套结构。当前的 `root.iter()` 遍历所有元素，包括嵌套在 `<IrcutFilter>` 块中的元素，所以 `IrcutFilterType` 应该能被找到。\n\n让我确认一下 `IrcutFilterType` 的完整路径：\n- 它在 `<IrcutFilter>` 块内，不在根级别\n\n但 `root.iter()` 会遍历所有元素，包括嵌套的，所以 `tag == \"IrcutFilterType\"` 应该能匹配到。\n\n好的，让我确认这个修复方案。\n\n最终修复方案：\n1. `get_filter_settings`：将 `irCutFilter` 改为 `IrcutFilterType`\n2. `set_filter_settings`：将 `irCutFilter` 改为 `IrcutFilterType`\n3. `dayNightMode` 保持不变（字段不存在，返回 unknown）\n\n这样：\n- IR 滤镜开关可以工作\n- 日夜模式开关无法工作（需要用户确认如何处理）\n\n或者，我可以将 `dayNightMode` 映射到 `IrcutFilterType`（如果日夜模式开关控制的是同一个功能）。\n\n但老板说\"禁止过度开发\"，我应该只修复字段名不匹配的问题。\n\n让我执行修复。\n\n等等，我还需要确认 `set_filter_settings` 中的 XML 修改逻辑是否正确。\n\n当前的代码：\n```python\nif day_night:\n    xml_str = re.sub(\n        r'(<dayNightMode>)[^<]*(</dayNightMode>)',\n        f'\\\\g<1>{day_night}\\\\g<2>',\n        xml_str\n    )\nif ir_cut:\n    xml_str = re.sub(\n        r'(<irCutFilter>)[^<]*(</irCutFilter>)',\n        f'\\\\g<1>{ir_cut}\\\\g<2>',\n        xml_str\n    )\n```\n\n需要改为：\n```python\nif day_night:\n    xml_str = re.sub(\n        r'(<dayNightMode>)[^<]*(</dayNightMode>)',\n        f'\\\\g<1>{day_night}\\\\g<2>',\n        xml_str\n    )\nif ir_cut:\n    xml_str = re.sub(\n        r'(<IrcutFilterType>)[^<]*(</IrcutFilterType>)',\n        f'\\\\g<1>{ir_cut}\\\\g<2>',\n        xml_str\n    )\n```\n\n这样应该可以工作。\n\n但是，`dayNightMode` 仍然不存在于 XML 中，所以修改无效。\n\n我是否应该删除 `dayNightMode` 的处理？\n\n不，老板说\"禁止过度开发\"，我不应该删除代码。我应该让 `dayNightMode` 保持原样（修改无效），只修复 `irCutFilter` 的字段名。\n\n这样：\n- IR 滤镜开关可以工作\n- 日夜模式开关仍然不工作（因为字段不存在）\n\n这是我能做的最精确的修复。\n\n好的，让我执行修复。\n\n但等等，我还需要考虑前端 HTML 的 data-value 值。\n\n前端按钮的值：\n- dayNightSwitch: day, night, auto\n- irCutSwitch: on, off, auto\n\nISAPI 的值：\n- IrcutFilterType: auto, on, off\n\n值映射：\n- \"auto\" → \"auto\" ✓\n- \"on\" → \"on\" ✓\n- \"off\" → \"off\" ✓\n\n值完全匹配，不需要转换。\n\n好的，让我执行修复。\n\n等等，我注意到 `IrcutFilterType` 在 XML 中是被嵌套在 `<IrcutFilter>` 块内的。\n\n```xml\n<IrcutFilter version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <IrcutFilterType>auto</IrcutFilterType>\n  <nightToDayFilterLevel>4</nightToDayFilterLevel>\n  <EventTrigger>\n    <eventType>IO</eventType>\n    <IrcutFilterAction>day</IrcutFilterAction>\n  </EventTrigger>\n</IrcutFilter>\n```\n\n`root.iter()` 会遍历所有元素，包括嵌套的，所以 `tag == \"IrcutFilterType\"` 应该能匹配到。\n\n但 `re.sub` 修改的是字符串，不是 XML 元素。如果 `IrcutFilterType` 不在根级别，`re.sub` 仍然可以匹配到。\n\n让我确认一下：\n- XML 字符串：`<IrcutFilterType>auto</IrcutFilterType>`\n- 正则表达式：`r'(<IrcutFilterType>)[^<]*(</IrcutFilterType>)'`\n- 替换：`<IrcutFilterType>{value}</IrcutFilterType>`\n\n这应该可以工作，因为 `re.sub` 会在整个字符串中搜索匹配。\n\n好的，让我执行修复。\n\n另外，我还需要修改 `get_filter_settings` 返回的数据结构。当前返回的是：\n```json\n{\n  \"dayNightMode\": \"unknown\",\n  \"irCutFilter\": \"auto\"\n}\n```\n\n如果 `dayNightMode` 不存在，它仍然是 \"unknown\"。\n\n前端 `updateSwitchHighlight('dayNightSwitch', 'unknown')` 会尝试匹配 `data-value=\"unknown\"` 的按钮，但不存在，所以不会添加 `active` 类。\n\n这会导致\"日夜模式\"开关不亮。\n\n但这是预期的，因为 `dayNightMode` 字段不存在。\n\n让我执行修复。\n\n等等，我还需要修改 `get_filter_settings` 中的字段名。当前代码：\n```python\nif tag == \"irCutFilter\":\n    ir_cut = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n```\n\n需要改为：\n```python\nif tag == \"IrcutFilterType\":\n    ir_cut = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\n```\n\n好的，让我执行修复。\n\n实际上，我还有一个问题：后端代码中还有其他地方使用了 `irCutFilter`（例如日志、返回数据结构等）。我需要确保只修改必要的部分。\n\n让我检查一下所有使用 `irCutFilter` 的地方。\n\n实际上，让我先读取完整的代码，确认所有需要修改的地方。\n\n然后一次性修改。\n\n好的，让我开始修复。老板，我确认找到了根因：\n\n**设备返回的 XML 中没有 `irCutFilter` 字段，实际字段是 `IrcutFilterType`**\n\n让我精确修复后端 `router.py`：<|tool_calls_section_begin|><|tool_call_begin|>functions.edit:243<|tool_call_argument_begin|>{\"edits\": [{\"newText\": \"            if tag == \\\"dayNightMode\\\":\\n                day_night = (elem.text or \\\"\\\").strip()\\n            elif tag == \\\"IrcutFilterType\\\":\\n                ir_cut = (elem.text or \\\"\\\").strip()\", \"oldText\": \"            if tag == \\\"dayNightMode\\\":\\n                day_night = (elem.text or \\\"\\\").strip()\\n            elif tag == \\\"irCutFilter\\\":\\n                ir_cut = (elem.text or \\\"\\\").strip()\"}, {\"newText\": \"        if ir_cut:\\n            xml_str = re.sub(\\n                r'(<IrcutFilterType>)[^<]*(</IrcutFilterType>)',\\n                f'\\\\g<1>{ir_cut}\\\\g<2>',\\n                xml_str\\n            )\", \"oldText\": \"        if ir_cut:\\n            xml_str = re.sub(\\n                r'(<irCutFilter>)[^<]*(</irCutFilter>)',\\n                f'\\\\g<1>{ir_cut}\\\\g<2>',\\n                xml_str\\n            )\"}], \"path\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\admin\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\dev-factory\\\\astrohub\\\\src\\\\api\\\\router.py\"}<|tool_call_end|><|tool_calls_section_end|>","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The user wants me to fix the issue precisely. Let me verify what I've done:\n\n1. I found that the ISAPI XML returned by the device uses `<IrcutFilterType>` instead of `<irCutFilter>`\n2. The `dayNightMode` field doesn't exist in the XML\n3. I've modified the backend code to use `IrcutFilterType` instead of `irCutFilter`\n\nBut the user said \"禁止过度开发\" and wants me to be precise. Let me also check if I need to:\n1. Update the version number (v8.50 already set)\n2. Verify the fix\n\nLet me also check the `set_filter_settings` endpoint to make sure the `dayNightMode` field is also handled correctly.\n\nActually, the user might be waiting for me to finish the fix and report. Let me verify the changes are correct and report.\n\nWait, the user said \"修改，精确修复，禁止过度开发！禁止绕弯路实现，禁止打补丁开发\". This means:\n1. Only modify what's necessary\n2. Don't add extra features or logging\n3. Fix the root cause, not add workarounds\n\nI've already modified the backend to use the correct field name `IrcutFilterType`. Let me also check if there's anything else needed.\n\nFor the `dayNightMode` field, since it doesn't exist in the XML, the current behavior (returning \"unknown\") is technically correct - the field doesn't exist. However, the user has a \"日夜模式\" switch in the UI that expects `dayNightMode` values.\n\nLooking at the ISAPI documentation, the `IrcutFilterType` field controls the IR filter mode (auto/on/off), which is essentially the day/night mode. But the user has two separate switches: \"日夜模式\" (day/night/auto) and \"IR 滤镜\" (on/off/auto).\n\nIf `dayNightMode` doesn't exist, I should:\n1. Either remove it (but that's changing logic beyond the scope)\n2. Or document that it doesn't exist in this device's ISAPI response\n\nBut the user said \"禁止过度开发\" and \"禁止绕弯路\". The most precise fix is just to change the field name for `irCutFilter` to `IrcutFilterType` and leave `dayNightMode` as is (returning \"unknown\").\n\nWait, but the user also complained about \"日夜模式\" switch not working. If `dayNightMode` doesn't exist, that switch will never work with this device. I need to inform the user of this.\n\nBut let me first check if `dayNightMode` might exist under a different name or in a different location.\n\nLooking at the ISAPI XML again:\n```xml\n<IrcutFilter version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <IrcutFilterType>auto</IrcutFilterType>\n  <nightToDayFilterLevel>4</nightToDayFilterLevel>\n  <EventTrigger>\n    <eventType>IO</eventType>\n    <IrcutFilterAction>day</IrcutFilterAction>\n  </EventTrigger>\n</IrcutFilter>\n```\n\nThere's no `dayNightMode` field. The closest is `IrcutFilterType` which controls the IR filter (day/night mode).\n\nSo `IrcutFilterType` = \"auto\" means automatic switching between day and night mode.\n`IrcutFilterType` = \"on\" means forced IR filter on (night mode).\n`IrcutFilterType` = \"off\" means forced IR filter off (day mode).\n\nAnd `IrcutFilterAction` = \"day\" means currently in day mode (IR filter is off).\n\nSo the mapping is:\n- `IrcutFilterType` controls the mode setting (auto/on/off)\n- `IrcutFilterAction` shows the current state (day/night)\n\nFor the \"日夜模式\" switch (day/night/auto), the values should map to `IrcutFilterType`:\n- \"auto\" → \"auto\"\n- \"day\" → \"off\" (IR filter off = day mode)\n- \"night\" → \"on\" (IR filter on = night mode)\n\nBut wait, the current backend code expects `dayNightMode` to have values \"day\", \"night\", \"auto\". But `IrcutFilterType` has values \"auto\", \"on\", \"off\".\n\nSo there's a value mapping issue too:\n- \"day\" (UI) → \"off\" (ISAPI)\n- \"night\" (UI) → \"on\" (ISAPI)\n- \"auto\" (UI) → \"auto\" (ISAPI)\n\nBut the user said \"禁止过度开发\" and \"禁止绕弯路\". I should not re-engineer the value mapping. I should just fix the field name and tell the user about the value mismatch.\n\nActually, let me re-read the user's message: \"修改，精确修复，禁止过度开发！禁止绕弯路实现，禁止打补丁开发\"\n\nThis means:\n1. Fix only what's broken\n2. Don't add extra features\n3. Don't add workarounds or patches\n\nThe most precise fix is:\n1. Change `irCutFilter` → `IrcutFilterType` in the backend\n2. Leave `dayNightMode` as is (it will continue to return \"unknown\" because the field doesn't exist)\n3. Inform the user that `dayNightMode` doesn't exist in the ISAPI response\n\nBut wait, the user also said \"日夜模式\" switch doesn't work. If `dayNightMode` doesn't exist, that switch will never work with this device.\n\nLet me check if maybe the `dayNightMode` is stored in a different field. Let me look at the full XML more carefully.\n\nActually, from the XML:\n```xml\n<IrcutFilterType>auto</IrcutFilterType>\n```\n\nThis is the only field that controls day/night mode. There's no separate `dayNightMode` field.\n\nSo the conclusion is:\n- `dayNightMode` field doesn't exist in this device's ISAPI response\n- `IrcutFilterType` is the correct field for controlling day/night mode\n\nThe user needs to decide how to handle this. But since they said \"禁止绕弯路\", I should just fix the field name and report the issue.\n\nActually, looking at this more carefully, the `dayNightMode` might be in a different ISAPI endpoint. Let me check if there's a separate endpoint for day/night mode.\n\nBut the user said \"禁止过度开发\", so I shouldn't go down that rabbit hole. I should just fix the `irCutFilter` field name and report that `dayNightMode` doesn't exist.\n\nHowever, the user explicitly asked for both \"日夜模式\" and \"IR 滤镜\" switches to work. If `dayNightMode` doesn't exist, I need to explain this.\n\nLet me just complete the fix and report. I've already modified the `irCutFilter` → `IrcutFilterType`. Let me also check if there are any other places in the code that reference `irCutFilter`.\n\nLet me also verify the edit was applied correctly.</think>用户要求精确修复，禁止过度开发。我已经修改了 `irCutFilter` → `IrcutFilterType`。\n\n让我验证修改是否正确，然后汇报："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:244","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py\" -Pattern \"irCutFilter|IrcutFilterType\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":254771,"output":7180,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":261951,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783286274999,"responseId":"cht000d40d4@dx19f3425369829bb503"}}
