{"type":"message","id":"2f43d711","parentId":"3d819000","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:21:18.339Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is telling me to fix the issue precisely. Let me look at what I found:\n\n1. The actual XML from the device has `<IrcutFilterType>auto</IrcutFilterType>` - not `irCutFilter`\n2. There is NO `dayNightMode` field in the XML\n3. My previous edit didn't apply - the code still has `irCutFilter` everywhere\n\nLet me do a precise fix - change ONLY the XML tag names in the parsing and regex substitution code. I need to modify router.py at lines 3698, 3705, and 3752.\n\nWait, looking at the Select-String output, my edits didn't apply. \n\nNow I need to find the exact code in the file and make the changes myself.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我的编辑没有生效。让我重新精确修复：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_82de6f9cc693447e9711e47d","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":3690,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":260,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":52017,"totalTokens":52283,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783286470578,"responseId":"msg_09489522-a82c-400f-ad54-1366771ef2ad"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f268f85","parentId":"2f43d711","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:21:18.356Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_82de6f9cc693447e9711e47d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n        day_night = \"unknown\"\r\n        ir_cut = \"unknown\"\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag == \"dayNightMode\":\r\n                day_night = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\r\n            elif tag == \"irCutFilter\":\r\n                ir_cut = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\r\n\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": True,\r\n            \"data\": {\r\n                \"dayNightMode\": day_night,\r\n                \"irCutFilter\": ir_cut\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取滤镜设置异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.put(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/filter\", summary=\"设置滤镜与日夜模式\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_filter_settings(device_id: str, body: dict) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置 dayNightMode 和/或 irCutFilter。\r\n\r\n    请求体:\r\n        {\"dayNightMode\": \"day|night|auto\", \"irCutFilter\": \"on|off|auto\"}\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    day_night = body.get(\"dayNightMode\", \"\")\r\n    ir_cut = body.get(\"irCutFilter\", \"\")\r\n\r\n    # 先 GET 当前完整 XML，再修改对应字段后 PUT\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = await asyncio.to_thread(client.get, \"/Image/channels/1\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取当前设置失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        xml_str = resp.xml\r\n        import re\r\n\r\n        if day_night:\r\n            xml_str = re.sub(\r\n                r'(<dayNightMode>)[^<]*(</dayNightMode>)',\r\n                f'\\\\g<1>{day_night}\\\\g<2>',\r\n                xml_str\r\n            )\r\n        if ir_cut:\r\n            xml_str = re.sub(\r\n                r'(<irCutFilter>)[^<]*(</irCutFilter>)',\r\n                f'\\\\g<1>{ir_cut}\\\\g<2>',\r\n                xml_str\r\n            )\r\n\r\n        put_resp = await asyncio.to_thread(client.put, \"/Image/channels/1\", xml_str)\r\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            log_info(\"image\", \"filter\", {\"device\": device_id, \"dayNight\": day_night, \"irCut\": ir_cut})\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"滤镜设置成功\"}\r\n        else:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置失败: HTTP {put_resp.status_code}\"}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置滤镜异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n# === 慢快门 DSS (v8.45) ===\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter\", summary=\"获取慢快门设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\n\n[610 more lines in file. Use offset=3770 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783286478356}}
