{"type":"message","id":"5c22e407","parentId":"3bb41fed","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:23:33.340Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\nWait, this is getting too complex. Let me take a simpler approach - read the file, make targeted line replacements.老板说得对，我绕弯路了。最简单的方法：直接看 ISAPI 文档，确认字段名，然后精确修改。\n\n从 xlsx 文档：\n- `ircutFilter` (小写 ircut)\n\n但后端代码用了 `irCutFilter`（驼峰）。\n\n**精确修复：只改一个字段名**\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ba5067837ea44f26aaf8ee02","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nwith open('C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/api/router.py', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# 精确替换：只改字段名\ncontent = content.replace('tag == \\\"irCutFilter\\\"', 'tag == \\\"ircutFilter\\\"')\ncontent = content.replace('body.get(\\\"irCutFilter\\\"', 'body.get(\\\"ircutFilter\\\"')\ncontent = content.replace('\\\"irCutFilter\\\": ir_cut', '\\\"ircutFilter\\\": ir_cut')\ncontent = content.replace('(<irCutFilter>)', '(<ircutFilter>)')\ncontent = content.replace('(</irCutFilter>)', '(</ircutFilter>)')\n\nwith open('C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/api/router.py', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(content)\n\nprint('Done')\n\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_c44a74d91cfa40d886fef42c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nwith open('C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub/src/api/router.py', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# 精确替换：只改字段名\ncontent = content.replace('tag == \\\"irCutFilter\\\"', 'tag == \\\"ircutFilter\\\"')\ncontent = content.replace('body.get(\\\"irCutFilter\\\"', 'body.get(\\\"ircutFilter\\\"')\ncontent = content.replace('\\\"irCutFilter\\\": ir_cut', '\\\"ircutFilter\\\": ir_cut')\ncontent = content.replace('(<irCutFilter>)', '(<ircutFilter>)')\ncontent = content.replace('(</irCutFilter>)', '(</ircutFilter>)')\n\nwith open('C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/