*\n- 前端发送：`{ dss_level: val }` ✓\n- 后端接收：`body.get(\"dss_level\", \"\")` ✓\n- 后端构造 XML：`<DSS><enabled>true</enabled><DSSLevel>*4</DSSLevel></DSS>` ✓\n- 后端 PUT 到：`/Image/channels/1/DSS` ✓\n\n**字段名匹配正常。**\n\n但你说\"点击后没有应用结果\"，这说明 PUT 请求可能失败了。\n\n**需要验证：**\n直接调用 ISAPI 测试 PUT `/Image/channels/1/DSS` 是否生效。但我在跑测试脚本时遇到了 import 路径问题。\n\n需要我重新写测试脚本验证吗？或者你有其他信息？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":101328,"output":2592,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103920,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783287647085,"responseId":"cht000dab54@dx19f343a230d2872503"}}
