{"type":"message","id":"2d87bdaf","parentId":"ea022252","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:42:11.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\nThe test shows that:\n1. DSS PUT to the device works - status 200, and the value changed from *4 to *8\n2. So the ISAPI device accepts DSS level changes correctly\n\nBut the user says \"点击后没有应用任何结果\" - clicking the dropdown doesn't apply anything\n\nThe slow shutter code flow:\n- Frontend sends PUT to `/api/v1/ptz/{device_ip}/image/slow-shutter` with `{ dss_level: val }`\n- Backend receives this, constructs XML, PUTs to `/Image/channels/1/DSS`\n- Device returns 200\n\nThe direct ISAPI test shows the device accepts the change. So the issue must be:\n1. Frontend API call not reaching the backend?\n2. Backend endpoint returning error?\n\nLet me test the backend endpoint directly via HTTP.老板，慢快门 PUT 到设备是成功的！从 *4 改到了 *8。\n\n问题不在设备端。让我测试后端 API 端点是否正常：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_c8c2118ab6514b2fa88e2da8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory && python test_dss.py","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_28536dd80b7544ada44a0f93","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"import urllib.request, json; req = urllib.request.Request('http://127.0.0.1:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/image/slow-shutter', data=json.dumps({'dss_level': '*8'}).encode(), headers={'Content-Type': 'application/json'}, method='PUT'); resp = urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=15); print(resp.read().decode())\" 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_30c059afb17c468faa8cead0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"import urllib.request, json; req = urllib.request.Request('http://127.0.0.1:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/image/slow-shutter', data=json.dumps({'dss_level': '*8'}).encode(), headers={'Content-Type': 'application/json'}, method='PUT'); resp = urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=15); print(resp.read().decode())\""}},{"typ