{"type":"message","id":"a9d493b4","parentId":"8a79def0","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:42:27.634Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"下拉菜单显示正常，获取正常，但是下拉菜单点击后没有应用任何结果\".\n\nFrom the test results:\n1. Direct ISAPI test: PUT to `/Image/channels/1/DSS` returns 200, value changes from *4 to *8 - **device accepts changes**\n2. Backend API test: PUT to `/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/image/slow-shutter` with `{dss_level: \"*8'}` returns `{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"*8'}` - **backend works**\n3. But wait - I also see `{\"success\":false,\"message\":\"... HTTP 0\"}` in one result\n\nThe issue is NOT the backend. The backend works. The device works.\n\nThe user said \"点击后没有应用任何结果\". This is a frontend issue.\n\nLet me think about what could be wrong with the frontend:\n1. The dropdown value is `*4`, but maybe the option value doesn't match?\n2. The `setSlowShutter` function might not be called?\n3. The `apiPut` might fail?\n\nWait, the user said \"获取正常\" - the GET works, meaning the dropdown loads the current value correctly.\n\"点击后没有应用\" - clicking the dropdown doesn't apply the change.\n\nLet me check the frontend `setSlowShutter` function and the dropdown `onchange` handler.\n\nActually, I should check if there's an `onchange` handler on the select element, or if it's using an event listener.\n\nLet me search for `slowShutterSelect` in the HTML.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"后端 API 和设备都正常！让我检查前端事件绑定：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:173","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"slowShutterSelect\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line -First 15"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":107438,"output":412,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107850,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason