{"type":"message","id":"ed9a64fc","parentId":"af72503a","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:52:08.636Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"备份成功了。现在我需要：\n\n1. 回滚调试日志 - 删除 setSlowShutter 中的 console.log\n2. 找到 operationLog 函数\n3. 找到媒体信息显示的代码\n4. 找到\"最新消息第一行\"的逻辑\n\n让我先回滚调试日志。\n\n我需要把：\n```javascript\nfunction setSlowShutter(val) {\n    console.log('[SLOW SHUTTER] Called with value:', val);\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) {\n        console.warn('[SLOW SHUTTER] No connected device');\n        return;\n    }\n```\n\n改回：\n```javascript\nfunction setSlowShutter(val) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n```\n\n然后我需要找到 operationLog 的定义和媒体信息的代码。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"备份完成（backup_20260706_055132）。\n\n**1. 回滚调试日志：**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a1420562c91645cd8bafc60e","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"function setSlowShutter(val) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;","oldText":"function setSlowShutter(val) {\n    console.log('[SLOW SHUTTER] Called with value:', val);\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) {\n        console.warn('[SLOW SHUTTER] No connected device');\n        return;\n    }"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":94616,"output":370,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94986,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783288292699,"responseId":"cht000d829b@dx19f3443e97229c2503"}}
