{"type":"message","id":"ee75f2c2","parentId":"68a139f4","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:52:57.081Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_8c03a00e9abd4bde8285c741","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        }\r\n        // Logging\r\n        function addLog(level, msg) {\r\n            var c = document.getElementById('logContainer');\r\n            if (!c) return;\r\n            var d = document.createElement('div');\r\n            d.className = 'log-entry ' + level;\r\n            d.textContent = '[' + new Date().toLocaleTimeString() + '] ' + msg;\r\n            c.insertBefore(d, c.firstChild);\r\n            if (c.children.length > 50) c.removeChild(c.lastChild);\r\n        }\r\n        // WebSocket\r\n        function connectWS() {\r\n            try {\r\n                var ws = new WebSocket(WS_URL);\r\n                ws.onopen = function() {\r\n                    addLog('info', 'WebSocket 已连接');\r\n                };\r\n                ws.onclose = function() {\r\n                    setTimeout(connectWS, 3000);\r\n                };\r\n                ws.onmessage = function(e) {\r\n                    try {\r\n                        var data = JSON.parse(e.data);\r\n                        if (data.type === 'health') updateHealth(data);\r\n                    } catch(err) {}\r\n                };\r\n            } catch(e) {\r\n                addLog('warn', 'WebSocket 连接失败');\r\n            }\r\n\n[1990 more lines in file. Use offset=1118 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783288377081}}
{"type":"message","id":"c53b74c0","parentId":"ee75f2c2","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:52:57.081Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_ae778804da1b4f4ea1e5aa19","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    }\r\n\r\n    // 媒体信息日志(输出到左侧 mediaLogBox)\r\n    function mediaLog(msg, type) {\r\n        var colors = { 'info': '#8b949e', 'success': '#3fb950', 'error': '#f85149', 'warning': '#d29922' };\r\n        var color = colors[type] || '#8b949e';\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('mediaLogBox');\r\n        if (!box) return;\r\n        var entry = document.createElement('div');\r\n        entry.style.cssText = 'color:' + color + ';font-size:11px;font-family:monospace;line-height:1.4;margin-bottom:2px';\r\n        entry.textContent = msg;\r\n        box.appendChild(entry);\r\n        while (box.children.length > 100) box.removeChild(box.firstChild);\r\n        box.scrollTop = box.scrollHeight;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    // 媒体输入状态更新\r\n    function updateMediaInputStatus(state) {\r\n        var dot = document.getElementById('mediaInputDot');\r\n        var status = document.getElementById('mediaInputStatus');\r\n        if (!dot || !status) return;\r\n        if (state === 'playing') {\r\n            dot.className = 'status-dot green';\r\n            status.textContent = '媒体输入: 已连接';\r\n        } else if (state === 'connecting') {\r\n            dot.className = 'status-dot yellow';\r\n            status.textContent = '媒体输入: 连接中';\r\n        } else {\r\n            dot.className = 'status-dot red';\r\n            status.textContent = '媒体输入: 等待连接';\r\n\n[338 more lines in file. Use offset=2770 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783288377081}}
{"type":"message","id":"174230c3","parentId":"c53b74c0","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:53:18.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我看到了三个日志函数：\n\n**1. `addLog` (index.html L1090)** — 已经是最新在第一行 ✓\n```javascript\nc.insertBefore(d, c.firstChild);  // 最新在第一行\nif (c.children.length > 50) c.removeChild(c.lastChild);  // 移除最后一个\n```\n\n**2. `operationLog` (index.html L1592)** — 最新在末尾 ❌\n```javascript\nbox.appendChild(entry);  // 最新在末尾\nif (box.children.length > 50) box.removeChild(box.firstChild);  // 移除第一个\n```\n\n**3. `mediaLog` (index.html L2743)** — 最新在末尾 ❌\n```javascript\nbox.appendChild(entry);  // 最新在末尾\nwhile (box.children.length > 100) box.removeChild(box.firstChild);  // 移除第一个\nbox.scrollTop = box.scrollHeight;  // 滚动到底部\n```\n\n需要修改：\n- `operationLog`: `appendChild` → `insertBefore(firstChild)`, `removeChild(firstChild)` → `removeChild(lastChild)`\n- `mediaLog`: 同上，并移除 `scrollTop = scrollHeight`\n\n然后还需要把慢快门信息加入日志写入和媒体信息文字输出。\n\n现在让我看看 console.html 中 `setSlowShutter` 的代码，看看它是否已经有 `operationLog` 调用。从之前的搜索结果，我看到：\n```\n1688: if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('慢快门: ' + r.message, 'success');\n```\n\n所以 `setSlowShutter` 已经有 `operationLog` 调用了。但用户说\"没有应用任何结果\"，这说明 `operationLog` 可能没有被调用到，或者 `apiPut` 失败了。\n\n但用户现在要求的是：\n1. 回滚调试日志 ✓\n2. 慢快门信息加入日志写入和媒体信息文字输出\n3. 日志顺序改为最新第一行\n\n让我先检查 `setSlowShutter` 的完整代码，看看它是否已经有 `mediaLog` 调用。从之前的读取：\n```javascript\nfunction setSlowShutter(val) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    apiPut('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/slow-shutter', { dss_level: val }).then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            showToast('success', r.message);\n            if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('慢快门: ' + r.message, 'success');\n            var sel = document.getElementById('slowShutterSelect');\n            if (sel) sel.value = val;\n        } else {\n            showToast('error', '慢快门设置失败: ' + (r ? r.message : '未知错误'));\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        showToast('error', '慢快门请求异常: ' + e.message);\n        loadSlowShutter(dev);\n    });\n}\n```\n\n已经有 `operationLog` 调用了。但用户要求\"加入日志写入和媒体信息文字输出\"。\n\n这意味着：\n1. 操作日志：已经有 `operationLog` 调用 ✓\n2. 媒体信息：需要添加 `mediaLog` 调用\n3. 日志写入：可能需要添加 `addLog` 调用\n\n但 `mediaLog` 和 `addLog` 在 `index.html` 中定义，`setSlowShutter` 在 `console.html` 中。由于 `console.html` 是通过 includes 包含在 `index.html` 中的，所以 `mediaLog` 和 `addLog` 应该可以在 `console.html` 中访问。\n\n让我检查 `setSlowShutter` 的完整代码，然后添加 `mediaLog` 调用。\n\n同时，我还需要检查 `loadSlowShutter` 是否有日志输出。\n\n从之前的搜索结果：\n```\n1689: if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('慢快门: ' + r.message, 'success');\n```\n\n所以 `setSlowShutter` 成功时已经有 `operationLog`。但失败时没有。让我也添加失败时的日志。\n\n同时，用户要求\"慢快门所有的这些信息，加入日志写入，加入媒体信息的文字输出\"。这意味着：\n1. `setSlowShutter` 成功 → `operationLog` + `mediaLog`\n2. `setSlowShutter` 失败 → `operationLog` + `mediaLog`\n3. `loadSlowShutter` 加载完成 → `mediaLog`\n\n让我现在执行修改。\n\n现在我看清了所有需要修改的内容。让我执行：\n\n**修改清单：**\n1. `operationLog` (index.html L1592): `appendChild` → `insertBefore`, `removeChild(firstChild)` → `removeChild(lastChild)`\n2. `mediaLog` (index.html L2743): 同上，移除 `scrollTop`\n3. `setSlowShutter` (console.html L1682): 添加 `mediaLog` 调用\n4. 版本号迭代"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_878eaa5f43c540eda82fdafb","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"            box.insertBefore(entry, box.firstChild);\n            if (box.children.length > 50) box.removeChild(box.lastChild);","oldText":"            box.appendChild(entry);\n            if (box.children.length > 50) box.removeChild(box.firstChild);"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8eebf60f87384986aae5d857","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        box.insertBefore(entry, box.firstChild);\n        while (box.children.length > 100) box.removeChild(box.lastChild);","oldText":"        box.appendChild(entry);\n        whil